240218
- Enabled manouvering during pitch trimming

231203
- Setting the pitch angle
  + Switch pitch trim on/off on function custom_6
  + rd_pitchRate: Rate with which he pitch is being integrated [deg/s]
- Zeroing of pitch angle on function custom_5 (right click on control button)
- Zeroing of pitch angle when arming (if disarmed before)
- Zeroing of pitch angle when enabling MANUAL mode


*** Instructions: ***
- Change pitch trim angle
	* Press Shift+Depth_Hold (Buttons 1+2)
	* Check output window

22.08.2023 - Version 4.1.5


02.07.2023 - Version 4.1.4
Motor coefficients are loaded from parameters

