*** Good to know: ***

Upload binary via USB
	./waf --upload sub

Debug output on QGCS:
	gcs().send_text(MAV_SEVERITY_INFO, "Relay / Optocoupler OFF");

Access parameters:
	g.rd_fwd_cmd_RM_T